item.title: Logging in
item.dc:creator: @Lirimoo Lirimoo
item.description:

Do you use uTorrent to portforward ?..
uTorrent closes your connect to localhost, so you cant connect to your own Server.
Close uTorrent and then connect, IF YOURE USING.
